*Jadna* devojčica je uplakana stajala na uglu.(The poor girl was standing sadly at the corner.)

Čovek je video *jadnu* ženu prosjaka i pružio joj novac.(The man saw the poor beggar woman and gave her money.)

*Jadno* dete je bilo gladno i odjednom je zaplakalo.(The poor child was hungry and suddenly started crying.)

On je nazvao *jadno* stvorenje mrtvim.(He called the poor creature dead.)

Moj komšija je živeo u *jadnoj* kući.(My neighbor was living in a poor house.)

Učiteljica je pogledala *jadnu* učenicu i osetila žalost.(The teacher looked at the poor student and felt sorrow.)